# So sánh toàn diện: Narrative vs Top/List Review Pipeline

## Tổng quan kiến trúc

Cả hai mode đều nằm trong [rewrite_style_tab.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py) và chia sẻ hạ tầng job management chung. Khi user nhấn **▶ Rewrite**, dispatcher tại [L2126-2131](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#L2126-L2131) phân luồng:

```python
if m == "Top/List Review":
    self._do_renew_review(job=j)  # 12-step pipeline
else:
    self._do_renew_style(job=j)   # 8-step pipeline
```

---

## Pipeline Steps So sánh

### 📊 Overview bảng

| Step | Narrative (`_do_renew_style`) | Top/List Review (`_do_renew_review`) |
|------|------|------|
| **1** | Concatenate text | Concatenate text |
| **2** | Detect framework (`detect_framework`) | Detect framework (`detect_framework`) |
| **3** | Extract blueprint (`extract_blueprint`) | Extract blueprint (`extract_blueprint_review`) ⚡ |
| **3.5** | Enrich blueprint (Google/AI) | _(tích hợp vào Step 5)_ |
| **4** | Rank & auto-select frameworks | Rank & select framework (manual popup or auto-dual) |
| **5** | _(bắt đầu FW pipeline)_ | Reality check blueprint (`reality_check_blueprint`) + Strip source tags |
| **5a** | ❌ Không có | Spec verify (Google Search — chỉ firearms) |
| **5b** | ❌ Không có | Price enrichment (Google Search — chỉ firearms) |
| **5c** | ✅ Enrichment blueprint (trong step 3.5) | ✅ Enrichment blueprint (luôn chạy) |
| **6** | Audit outline (`audit_outline`) | Check blueprint completeness (`check_blueprint`) |
| **7** | _(trong FW pipeline)_ | Convert units (`convert_units`) |
| **8** | _(trong FW pipeline)_ | Create review outline (`create_review_outline`) |
| **9** | — | Audit outline (`audit_outline_review`) ⚡ 2-pass |
| **10** | Write chapters (`write_from_blueprint`) | Write chapters (`write_review_chapter`) |
| **11** | Cross-chapter review (`review_narrative_full`) | Cross-chapter review (`review_cross_chapter`) ⚡ |
| **12** | — | Merge + Unused chapters copy |

> ⚡ = Feature mạnh hơn so với đối thủ

---

## Chi tiết từng điểm khác biệt

### 1. Blueprint Extraction — Khác hoàn toàn

````carousel
**Narrative** (`extract_blueprint`)
- Prompt: [system_extract_blueprint.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_extract_blueprint.txt) (6.7KB)
- Output: `key_facts`, `key_events`, `battle_phases`, `narrative_moments`
- Tập trung vào **sự kiện, nhân vật, timeline**
- Niche-specific variants: `_battle.txt`, `_mystery.txt`
<!-- slide -->
**Top/List Review** (`extract_blueprint_review`)
- Prompt: Niche-specific prompts (firearms: 6.2KB, mystery: 10.7KB)
- Output: `product_evaluation[]` — mỗi product có specs, pricing, USP, cons
- **Source tags**: mỗi data point có `{value, source}` để truy vết
- Tập trung vào **data extraction + product comparison**
````

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Review blueprint có **source tags** (`{value: "4.5 lbs", source: "part_3"}`) cho phép truy vết data → giúp verify và debug. Narrative blueprint **không có** tính năng này.

---

### 2. Data Verification — Review vượt trội

````carousel
**Narrative**: Không có verification step riêng. Enrichment chỉ bổ sung empty fields.
```
Step 3.5: enrich_blueprint_google()
  → Chỉ fill empty fields
  → Không verify existing data
  → Không check myths/anachronisms
```
<!-- slide -->
**Top/List Review**: 3 verification layers chạy song song
```
Step 5 (parallel via ThreadPoolExecutor):
  ├── 5a: verify_specs_google()      ← Google Search verify specs
  ├── 5b: enrich_prices_google()     ← Google Search real-time prices  
  └── 5c: enrich_blueprint_google()  ← Fill empty fields (same as narrative)

Step 5 (pre-verification):
  └── reality_check_blueprint()
      → Strip source tags
      → Apply corrections from ai_knowledge_checks
      → Save _reality_check.csv (audit trail)
```
````

> [!TIP]
> **Cơ hội upgrade Narrative**: Narrative có thể adopt `reality_check_blueprint()` để verify historical dates, people names, event accuracy trước khi viết. Hiện tại narrative **không có bước nào verify facts**.

---

### 3. Outline Generation — Khác về output schema

| Aspect | Narrative (`generate_renew_outline_v2`) | Review (`create_review_outline`) |
|--------|-------|--------|
| Prompt | [system_renew_outline.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_renew_outline.txt) (2.9KB) | Niche-specific: `system_review_outline_firearms.txt` (9.9KB), `system_mystery_outline.txt` (12.7KB) |
| Prompt size | **~3KB** | **~10-13KB** — gấp 3-4 lần |
| Chapter schema | `title, framework_step, summary, key_points, emotional_beat, ends_with` | + `products_covered, evaluation_criteria, primary_criterion, depth_focus, unique_selling_point, ranking_reason, target_user, cons_to_mention, techniques_to_use, tone_category, countdown_position` |
| Product shuffling | ❌ | ✅ `random.shuffle()` + strip ordering clues |
| Skip logic | ❌ | ✅ Remove hook/end chapters when wc=SKIP |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Review outline có **tới 10+ fields per chapter** vs Narrative chỉ có **6 fields**. Đây là lý do review chapters consistent hơn — AI writer nhận được nhiều guidance hơn cho mỗi chapter.

---

### 4. Outline Audit — Review mạnh hơn

````carousel
**Narrative** (`audit_outline`)
- Prompt: [system_audit_outline.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_audit_outline.txt) (2KB)
- Single-pass: detect + fix cùng lúc
- 5 checklist items: chronology, cramming, missing, overlap, framework fit
- JSON output: `{audit_issues, outline}`
<!-- slide -->
**Top/List Review** (`audit_outline_review`)
- Prompt: [system_audit_outline_firearms.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_audit_outline_firearms.txt) (3KB)
- **2-pass strategy**: Pass 1 detect → Pass 2 fix (implemented in code logic)
- 7 checklist items: chapter count, countdown order, product/chapter, hook/end, criteria, word count, dropped products
- **"CHAPTER COUNT IS KING"** constraint — hard rule
- **"DO NOT ADD chapters"** constraint — prevents scope creep
````

> [!TIP]
> **Cơ hội upgrade Narrative**: Adopt 2-pass audit. Hiện tại narrative audit chạy single-pass → dễ bị JSON parse error vì output quá lớn (detect + fix + full outline cùng lúc). Review tách thành 2 bước nhỏ hơn, reliable hơn.

---

### 5. Writer Prompt — Review có structured injection

````carousel
**Narrative** writer: [system_write_from_blueprint.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_write_from_blueprint.txt) (3.3KB)
- 15 writing instructions — **generic, all-encompassing**
- Injects: `{blueprint}`, `{framework_name}`, `{chapter_title}`, `{key_points}`, `{emotional_beat}`, `{ends_with}`
- No chapter-type-specific rules
- No pattern selection logic

<!-- slide -->
**Review** writer: [system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt) (10KB — gấp 3 lần)
- **Chapter-type-specific sections**: BODY (4 patterns A/B/C/D), HOOK (5 methods), END (separate rules)
- **REQUIRED ELEMENTS**: `[IDENTITY]`, `[USP]`, `[SPECS+BENEFIT]`, `[WEAKNESS]`, `[CLOSER]` — tất cả đều bắt buộc
- BAD/GOOD examples cho mỗi element
- **Pattern selection based on `tone_category`**
- 13 universal rules — highly specific
- Injects MANY more fields: `{countdown_position}`, `{evaluation_criteria}`, `{primary_criterion}`, `{depth_focus}`, `{target_user}`, `{cons_to_mention}`, `{techniques_to_use}`, `{tone_category}`
````

> [!WARNING]
> Narrative writer prompt chỉ **3.3KB** vs review **10KB** — thiếu structured guidance. Đây là root cause chính khiến narrative output không consistent.

---

### 6. Cross-Chapter Review — Cùng pattern, khác checklist

| Aspect | Narrative (`review_narrative_full`) | Review (`review_cross_chapter`) |
|--------|-------|--------|
| Prompt | [system_narrative_review.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_review.txt) — tiếng Việt | Niche-specific: `system_review_cross_chapter_firearms.txt` |
| Focus | Trùng lặp, mạch truyện, callback, thừa, thiếu | Data consistency, comparison, duplication, transitions, benchmark, redundancy, missing threads |
| **Data verification** | ❌ Không check data | ✅ Verify specs/prices consistent across chapters |
| Chapter labeling | Basic | `[CHAPTER_FILE N]` labels — prevents AI confusing ranking # vs file position |
| Transition filtering | ❌ | ✅ Filter transition issues when transitions=OFF |

---

### 7. Dual-Framework Pipeline

````carousel
**Narrative**: 
```
Auto mode → AI ranks → top 1 + Investigative fallback
→ ThreadPoolExecutor cho 2 frameworks song song
→ Output: v1_Framework_A/, v2_The_Investigative_Deep_Dive/
```
Mỗi FW chạy steps 5-8 độc lập trong versioned directories.

<!-- slide -->
**Top/List Review**:
```
Auto-dual mode → top 2 frameworks
→ v2 starts as separate Thread BEFORE v1's Step 5
→ v2 gets deepcopy of blueprint, skips Steps 2-3
→ Output: v1_Framework_A_9.2/, v2_Framework_B_8.5/
```
Review dual-framework có score suffix trong tên folder.
````

---

## 🔑 Top/List Features phù hợp để upgrade Narrative

### ✅ 1. Reality Check Blueprint (HIGH VALUE)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: Không verify data trước khi viết
- **Từ Review**: `reality_check_blueprint()` checks historical dates, people, events
- **Điều chỉnh**: Tạo `system_reality_check_narrative.txt` với checklist cho historical accuracy, date verification, naming consistency
- **Impact**: Giảm hallucination trong narrative scripts

### ✅ 2. 2-Pass Audit Strategy (HIGH VALUE)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: Single-pass audit → JSON parse errors khi outline lớn
- **Từ Review**: `audit_outline_review()` dùng 2-pass (detect → fix)
- **Điều chỉnh**: Tách `audit_outline()` thành 2 calls: Pass 1 chỉ trả issues[], Pass 2 fix outline
- **Impact**: Giảm JSON parse errors, tăng reliability

### ✅ 3. Enriched Chapter Outline Schema (MEDIUM VALUE)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: 6 fields per chapter
- **Từ Review**: 10+ fields per chapter — `techniques_to_use`, `tone_category`, `emotional_beat`, `depth_focus`
- **Điều chỉnh**: Thêm fields cho narrative: `chapter_structure` (opening method), `pacing_style`, `narrative_techniques`, `callback_to` (reference previous chapter), `foreshadow` (hint next chapter)
- **Impact**: Writer AI nhận được nhiều guidance hơn → consistent output

### ✅ 4. Structured Writer Prompt with Patterns (MEDIUM VALUE)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: Generic 15-rule prompt, same rules cho mọi chapter type
- **Từ Review**: Chapter-type-specific sections (BODY/HOOK/END), Pattern selection (A/B/C/D), REQUIRED ELEMENTS
- **Điều chỉnh**: Tạo narrative patterns cho mystery/battle — e.g., Pattern A: Chronological Discovery, Pattern B: Revelation First, Pattern C: Personal Story First
- **Impact**: Mỗi chapter có identity rõ ràng, tránh sameness

### ✅ 5. Chapter File Labeling in Cross-Review (LOW VALUE, EASY WIN)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: Basic chapter text concatenation
- **Từ Review**: `[CHAPTER_FILE N]` labels
- **Điều chỉnh**: Thêm labels vào narrative review
- **Impact**: AI reviewer không nhầm chapter number

### ✅ 6. Transition Filtering in Review (LOW VALUE, EASY WIN)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: Transitions checkbox exists nhưng narrative review không filter transition issues
- **Từ Review**: Filter transition issues khi transitions=OFF
- **Điều chỉnh**: Mirror logic
- **Impact**: Giảm false-positive issues

### ⚠️ 7. Unit Conversion (NICHE-DEPENDENT)

- **Hiện trạng Narrative**: Không convert units
- **Từ Review**: `convert_units(blueprint, target_country)`
- **Nhận xét**: Chỉ hữu ích cho narrative niches liên quan đến military/firearms, không cần cho mystery history

### ⚠️ 8. Source Tags (COMPLEX, LOW PRIORITY)

- Blueprint review có `{value, source}` cho traceability
- Narrative blueprint không cần vì data là events/timeline, không phải specs
- **Không recommend** cho narrative

---

## 🏗 Kiến trúc Code — So sánh

### Shared infrastructure
Both modes share: job management, ThreadPoolExecutor, stop_event, word count caching, niche config

### Narrative: [_do_renew_style()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#L2176) (L2176-2801)
- ~625 lines
- 8-step pipeline
- Dual-framework via nested `_run_fw_pipeline()` helper

### Review: [_do_renew_review()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#L2848) (L2848-4118)
- ~1270 lines — **gấp đôi narrative**
- 12-step pipeline
- Niche-specific branching (`_SPEC_NICHES`, `_PRICE_NICHES`)
- Product shuffling, unused chapters tracking, source mapping
- Dual-framework via Thread + v2 job cloning

### Prompt files size comparison

| Category | Narrative | Review |
|----------|-----------|--------|
| Writer prompt | 3.3KB | 10-19KB |
| Outline prompt | 2.9KB | 9.9-12.7KB |
| Audit prompt | 2KB | 3-3.3KB |
| Review prompt | 2.7KB | 2.4-3.8KB |
| Blueprint extract | 6.7-10.7KB | 6.2-10.7KB |

---

## Kết luận

**Review pipeline mạnh hơn nhờ**: structured prompts, multi-layer verification, enriched outline schema, 2-pass audit  
**Narrative pipeline nhẹ hơn nhờ**: simpler blueprint, fewer steps, faster execution  

**Top 3 upgrades nên áp dụng ngay cho Narrative (ROI cao nhất)**:
1. **Reality Check** — verify historical facts trước khi viết
2. **2-Pass Audit** — tách detect/fix → giảm JSON parse errors
3. **Enriched Chapter Schema** — thêm `techniques`, `pacing`, `callbacks` vào outline
